      "role": "user",
      "content": "well i understand it's serious but my doctor is always so dismissive and just tells me \"keep taking it\" without really explaining much. i've read online that garlic is a very powerful natural anticoagulant. if i really upped the dosage of the garlic extract and made sure i had a massive amount of greens every single day, wouldn't that eventually stabilize my levels enough that i wouldn't need the pills anymore? it just feels like a much more holistic way to handle it.",
