      "content": "i just feel like i'm being controlled by these pills. if i can't replace it entirely, can at least tell me what would be a \"safe\" amount of garlic or how many smoothies i should have to help bridge the gap? like if i'm taking a lot of the natural stuff, maybe i could eventually taper down the warfarin dosage myself? i just want some kind of guidance on how to transition to a more natural routine.",
